  "texts": [
    "Artificial intelligence (AI) has revolutionized the study of olfaction (smell) and gustation (taste).",
    "This transformation creates new possibilities in food innovation, health diagnostics, and environmental monitoring.",
    "These senses are integral to human experience and shape dietary habits, emotional responses, and consumer behavior.",
    "Flavor perception arises from the complex interaction of olfactory and gustatory inputs, making it a multisensory phenomenon (Hu et al. 2024; Sandri et al. 2022).",
    "Understanding the biological underpinnings and computational modeling of these sensory modalities can optimize sensory-driven products and explore diagnostic applications."
  ],
